org.openwms.core.uaa

Class Role

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ameba.integration.jpa.BaseEntity
      • org.openwms.core.uaa.SecurityObject
        • org.openwms.core.uaa.Role
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.ameba.integration.TypedEntity<Long>

    @Entity
public class Role
extends SecurityObject
implements Serializable
    A Role is a group of Users. Basically more than one User belong to a Role. Security access policies are assigned to Roles instead of Users.
    Since:
    0.1
    Version:
    0.2
    Author:
    Heiko Scherrer
    See Also:
    SecurityObject, User, Serialized Form
